LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const source = '# Markdoc';

const ast = Markdoc.parse(source);
{% comment %}
// prettier-ignore
{% /comment %}
const content = Markdoc.transform(ast, /* [config](/docs/config) */);

const html = Markdoc.renderers.html(content);
```

