TITLE: Custom DateTime Attribute Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a custom DateTime attribute type with validation and transformation logic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/markdoc/docs/blob/main/pages/docs/attributes.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export class DateTime {
  validate(value, config) {
    if (typeof value !== 'string' || isNaN(Date.parse(value)))
      return [
        {
          id: 'invalid-datetime-type',
          level: 'critical',
          message: 'Must be a string with a valid date format'
        }
      ];

    return [];
  }

  transform(value, config) {
    return Date.parse(value);
  }
}
```

