TITLE: Implementing Custom Functions in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create custom function definitions for array inclusion checking and string uppercase conversion in Markdoc.
SOURCE: https://github.com/markdoc/docs/blob/main/pages/docs/functions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const includes = {
  transform(parameters) {
    const [array, value] = Object.values(parameters);

    return Array.isArray(array) ? array.includes(value) : false;
